data.description: This beautiful 2 story home located on a huge corner lot offers four bedrooms, two full baths, three half baths and both formals. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream with countless storage, stainless steel appliances and a large center island perfect for entertaining. The family room is the heart of the home, with a fireplace and floor-to-ceiling windows that fill the house with natural light. Outside, you'll find a sparkling pool and a detached guest suite along with two storage sheds and plenty of yard space. This home is offering the feeling of spaciousness and convenience as it's close to shopping and restaurants. Zoned to highly acclaimed CFISD schools. Recent HVAC 2023, Water Heater 2023, garbage disposal 2023, pex pipe in garage conversion, and Cool Deck coating around pool area in 2019. This home has it all! Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this beautiful, spacious home yours! Schedule your showing today!
